<h1>Breakpoints</h1>
<p>
	Fandom Design System uses <b>Mobile-first</b> approach.<br/>
	Use breakpoints to create responsive layout and components.<br/>
	To set breakpoints pick one of variables from table below and use it in <code>@media</code> query in scss file.
</p>
<p>
	Currently displayed breakpoint:<br/>
	<code class="variable-name rp-displayed-breakpoint rp-displayed-breakpoint__s-only">$breakpoint-s-only: only screen and (max-width:767px)</code>
	<code class="variable-name rp-displayed-breakpoint rp-displayed-breakpoint__m-only">$breakpoint-m-only: only screen and (min-width:768px) and (max-width:1023px)</code>
	<code class="variable-name rp-displayed-breakpoint rp-displayed-breakpoint__l-only">$breakpoint-l-only: only screen and (min-width:1024px) and (max-width:1083px)</code>
	<code class="variable-name rp-displayed-breakpoint rp-displayed-breakpoint__xl-only">$breakpoint-xl-only: only screen and (min-width:1084px) and (max-width:1595px)</code>
	<code class="variable-name rp-displayed-breakpoint rp-displayed-breakpoint__xxl-up">$breakpoint-xxl-up: only screen and (min-width:1596px)</code>
</p>
<p>
	<img src="/images/breakpoints.png" class="rp-breakpoints-visualisation">
</p>

